high_descs: Look down at the counter in between the two sinks.
Pick up the bar of soap in between the two sinks.
Move further away from the sinks and look at the cabinets below the sink.
open the cabinet door all the way to the left, put the soap in the cabinet to the right of the rag.
Walk to face the sink on the left side.
Pick up the bar of soap from the sink.
Move further away from the sinks and look at the cabinets below the sink.
Open the cabinet door, put the soap down to the left of the first bar of soap and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of soap to the cabinet below the sink.

high_descs: Look down and face the sink counter
Pick up the soap on the counter
Turn right then head to the cabinet on the left  side of the sink
Open the cabinet and put in the soap then close the cabinet
Go towards the left sink
Pick up the soap in the sink
Turn left then move backwards and face the cabinet below the sink
Open the cabinet and put in the soap then close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the two soap in the cabinet

high_descs: Take a step back from the sink
Pick up the soap bar from the counter between the sinks
Turn all-way around to face the cabinet below the sink
Open the left side of the  cabinet, put the soap inside it, and close the cabinet
Go back to the sink
Pick up the soap bar from the left sink
Turn all-way around to face the sink cabinet
Open the left side of the cabinet, put the soap inside, and close it
anns.task_desc: Put two soap bars inside the sink cabinet
